
Claims (sample Vaadin-Spring web application)

    - Vaadin-powered UI
    - Spring-powered backend
    - Spring security with HTTP digest auth
    - Active record-style data access with JPA 2 + simple service layer
    - AspectJ ITDs and compile-time weaving
    - Maven build with JRebel plugin
    
    TODO: Paging, i18n, UI component hiding per user's authorities (declarative?)

Note: This is WIP, subject to change at any time.
